{"data":[{"id":563118840,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8ce5ab373d18d3d1a02ecdd1631310d8","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":11,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563118840","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546183276,"updated_time":1546195326,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"nobody","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e之所以学术界的民粹很猖狂，而政治界的民粹（黄巢之流）默默无闻，完全是因为看到知识分子没有兵权，无理取闹，欺负老实人而已。尽管要真论起合法性来，后者比前者要高得多；前者无限趋近于零。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我完全不懂数学，但我相信高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想的难度，多半高于一个傻子一夜之间会唱全本的《格萨尔》（这种事不是依然有人信么）。为什么总会有人对这种事情抱有希望呢？大概是因为关于神迹的传说太多了。只要还有人信神，就还会有人相信自己一念之间就可以超越人类几千年的文明成果，这倒也不足为奇。只要有神，一切皆有可能，别说证明世界难题，连宣称自己是第二个弥赛亚的都会有一大票人信。但问题是，至少到目前为止，信神者还是有理由的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过，有些事情和天才无关。天才和巫师是有区别的。再有天才，也不可能在一夜之间看完了《格萨尔》，而要背会它，至少要先看一遍吧；这是需要贪时间进去的。解决数学难题不能靠灵机一动，它必然是一种劳动（自然科学的研究，预备性劳动占的比例可能更大些）。任何学术都是一种实践，不光人文学科如此，归根结底，自然科学也是如此，而实践必须要在一定的时间中展开。超时间的成就不属于凡人；它在道理上是说不通的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可以把话说死了：就算有某人蒙主启示，一觉醒来写出了哥德巴赫猜想的证明过程，那这个成果也不属于他，对他而言毫无意义。因为这不是实践得来的。成果是成果，他是他，让他讲出道理来，他就傻了。这和抄袭实际上是一回事。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想见梅菲斯特，请先变成浮士德再说。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（借题发挥，算是发表一下对民科的总的看法；按理说我这种文科生不该答这个问题的。）\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"之所以学术界的民粹很猖狂，而政治界的民粹（黄巢之流）默默无闻，完全是因为看到知识分子没有兵权，无理取闹，欺负老实人而已。尽管要真论起合法性来，后者比前者要高得多；前者无限趋近于零。我完全不懂数学，但我相信高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想的难度，多半…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=495\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdat